8 AS INTRODUCED
9 An Act relating to the Prohibition of Unfair Service
Agreements Act; amending Section 5, Chapter 148,
10 O.S.L. 2024 (16 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 305), which
relates to prohibited recording of unfair service
11 agreements; providing that a recorded unfair service
agreement or notice or memorandum shall not provide
12 actual or constructive notice against a residential
real estate owner or title company; providing if an
13 unfair service agreement or notice or memorandum is
recorded it is void; and providing an effective date.
14
15
16 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
17 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY Section 5, Chapter 148, O.S.L.
18 2024 (16 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 305), is amended to read as
19 follows:
20 Section 305. 1. Recording an unfair service agreement is
21 prohibited. No person shall record or cause to be recorded an
22 unfair service agreement or notice or memorandum thereof in this
23 state;
24
